summary: Mini-addon for great Svarog`s Fitness Body.
descriptionHtml:
Install this only if you have [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41443/?]Dream Girl[/url] body!

How to install:
1. Download the UNP Fitness Blender or UNP Fitness Blender - NARROW on the original mod's page.
2. Install it
3. Download DG file here
4. Extract folder from archive, and throw folder to place, where you install Fitness blender. Click "Yes", when ask to overwrite.
Enjoy!

Many thanks to Svarog for great [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16731/?]Fitness Body[/url],
to Akiro for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24828/?]Unbleak ENB[/url],
to Maevan2 for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/32986/?]Mature skin[/url] textures,
to Zonzai and Seren4XX for amazing [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36425/?]Real Girl Realistic Body Texture[/url](used on screenshots with some my modifications),
and, of course, to Petrovich for wonderful [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/41443/?]Dream Girl[/url] body
P.S. Sorry for bad English.
author: Svarog
